release 1:
internal commands:
- cd
- cd <dir>
- ls
- ls <dir>
- environ
- echo <cmd>
- help
- quit
- clear
- clr

release 2:
fork() and exec() all other statements.
bugs:
- parse escapes (\)

release 3:
batch files as args on startup,
the shell should exit after the script is done.

release 4:
io redirection using < and >, eg:
app arg1 arg < inputfile > outputfile
this includes ls, environ, echo and help.

release 5:
support background execution using ampersand(&).

release 6:
change the prompt to show the current dir name.
(should work)